data.description:
Beautiful 3 Bedroom + Office, 2 Bathroom home, located in the highly desirable neighborhood of The Acreage, just walks away from the new Town Center.Built in 2020, the house sits on 1.62 Acres on paved roads, and boasts the modern luxuries that will appease even the fussiest buyers. No HOA! Hurricane Impact Windows and Doors! 24'' Tiles throughout house! Soft Touch Cabinets! Stainless Steel Appliances! Smart Technology Washer/Dryer! Extended Circular Driveway, prepped for concrete or pavers! Underground Utilities! Portable Generator Hookup! My Q Smart Garage Technology! NEST (wifi) Smart Thermostat! ADT alarm with cameras, touch screen panel & tamper-proof contacts at doors and windows! Ring Camera! TV Cable wall mount in all bedrooms and family room! Anti-Pest control in-wall system! Action Water Treatment system! Brand new Well Pump!
Close to major highways and top rated schools!
Enjoy the best of both worlds as you live in a rural community, but are able to enjoy the benefits of the city! The home is a short walk to the new, upcoming Town Center. The new owners will be able to walk to newly built grocery/retail stores, health and wellness services, educational facilities, entertainment and fine dining.
Bring your horses, boats, and recreational vehicles! Oversized yard with ample space for pool and other projects!
